<p>
<note n="0680005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0680005">聖本首缺</note>
<note n="0680006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0680006">之四＝中二【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0680007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0680007">一＝七【聖】</note>
<note n="0680008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0680008">智＝知【三】【宮】【聖】＊</note>
